
Title: Addition on both sides of an equality
Tags: #algebra #iff #\mathbb{R}
\forall a : \mathbb{R} \forall b : \mathbb{R}
------------------------------
a = b
------------------------------
\forall c : \mathbb{R} a + c = b + c

Title: Subtraction on both sides of an equality
Tags: #algebra #iff #\mathbb{R}
\forall a : \mathbb{R} \forall b : \mathbb{R}
------------------------------
a = b
------------------------------
\forall c : \mathbb{R} a - c = b - c
